snippet.title: Jurassic World Aftermath: Part 2 - Announce Trailer | Oculus Quest Platform
snippet.description:
All-new dinosaur encounters abound in this thrilling return to Isla Nublar! 
 
Jurassic World Aftermath: Part 2 is the highly anticipated conclusion to the suspenseful VR survival adventure, Jurassic World Aftermath, based on Universal Pictures and Amblin Entertainment’s blockbuster film franchise. 
 
Available exclusively on the Oculus Quest platform on 30th September 2021. Find out more at http://www.jurassicworldaftermath.com/
